      "content": "Section 9 of the principal enactment is hereby amended in subsection (5) of that section, as follows :-\n(1) by the substitution, for the words \"any officer or other employee\", of the words \"any teacher, officer or other employee\"; and\n(2) by the substitution, for the words \"that officer or employee\", of the words \"that teacher, officer or employee\".",
      "footnotes": [
