      ]
    },
    {
      "section_number": "9B",
      "content": "(1) The seal of the Commission shall be in the custody of the Secretary of the Commission.\n(2) The seal of the Commission may be altered in such manner as may be determined by the Commission.\n(3) The seal of the Commission shall not be affixed to any instrument or document except in the presence of the Secretary and any member of the commission, both of whom shall sign the instrument or document in token of their presence.\"",
