    {
      "section_number": "17",
      "content": "Section 34 of the principal enactment is hereby amended as follows:\n(1) by the repeal of subsection (1) of that section and the substitution therefor, of the following subsection:-\n(1) (a) The Vice-Chancellor of a University shall be appointed for a term of three years by the President upon the recommendation of the Commission from a panel of three names recommended by the Council of that University.\n(b) The Vice-Chancellor of a University may be removed from office by the President, after consultation with the Commission.",
